{
  "stem": "17135.6",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was one of the finest brigades, tell her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was one of the finest brigades, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I was assigned to engineering corps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because I was in charge of the heavy equipment like tractors, bulldozers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then for-- for at least two months we were building anti-tank ditches around Tel Aviv.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because there was-- there were two armored brigades of the Iraqis in Lod airport.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Tel Aviv was constantly afraid that one night-- there was a main road, a good road to Tel Aviv.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they could have taken the city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Of course, they had equipment and we had nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the only way to stop them is to cut the-- the road on-- on-- on there. 50 points and cut it in half and build ditches so that-- that they couldn't pass.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And on the side, also were ditches where they couldn't pass.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's what we did for two months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Let me tell you how I came to America.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "While I was in Israel, while I still was in the kibbutz, in 1956, suddenly I get a letter from the prosecutor-general.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They found-- look, the Germans left behind so many documentation that I was in Sachsenhausen And at that time, they prepared the trail of the murderers of the SS of Sachsenhausen.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had a whole bunch of them arrested.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they found me, that I live in Israel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they invite me to be a witness.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the first thing, before I was a witness, they-- they-- they invited me to-- to a consul to identify some guys.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And at that time I still had a fantastic memory.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I found them all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I give them the names.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then I became a witness.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and in the trial I was three times.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
